Package com.amazonaws.services.kinesis.samples.stocktrades.writer

Example that puts dummy stock trade data into Amazon Kinesis Streams (see StockTradesWriter class).

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    StockTradeGenerator
    Generates random stock trades by picking randomly from a collection of stocks, assigning a random price based on the mean, and picking a random quantity for the shares.
    StockTradesWriter
    Continuously sends simulated stock trades to Kinesis

Package com.amazonaws.services.kinesis.samples.stocktrades.writer Description

Example that puts dummy stock trade data into Amazon Kinesis Streams (see StockTradesWriter class). This package should be used in conjunction with com.amazonaws.services.kinesis.samples.stocktrades.processor and is based on the Kinesis stock trader example found at http://docs.aws.amazon.com/streams/latest/dev/learning-kinesis-module-one.html
